## Phase 3: 陪伴系统 (P1)

### 3.1 陪伴 Rules

- [ ] **rules/companion/daily-checkin.md**
  ```markdown
  触发: 每日 8:00
  读取: current.daily, progress, identity.target
  输出: 个性化提醒
  写入: progress.streak, progress.last_checkin
  ```

- [ ] **rules/companion/weekly-review.md**
  ```markdown
  触发: 周日 20:00
  读取: current.week, roles
  输出: 周复盘引导
  写入: journal (weekly), current.week (下周)
  ```

- [ ] **rules/companion/weekly-planning.md**
  ```markdown
  触发: 用户主动 / 周复盘后
  读取: roles, roadmap.quarter, current.month
  输出: 大石头规划引导
  写入: current.week.rocks
  ```

- [ ] **rules/companion/monthly-review.md**
  ```markdown
  触发: 每月 1 日
  读取: current.month, roadmap.quarter
  输出: 月度复盘引导
  写入: journal (monthly), current.month (下月)
  ```

### 3.2 主动推送集成

- [ ] **proactive_worker.py** - 添加 lifecoach 触发器
  ```python
  # 每日签到
  if hour == 8 and has_lifecoach_data(user):
      trigger_daily_checkin(user)

  # 周复盘
  if weekday == 6 and hour == 20:  # 周日晚8点
      trigger_weekly_review(user)

  # 卡点检测
  if days_since_checkin >= 3:
      trigger_care_message(user)
  ```

- [ ] **reminders.yaml** - 添加 lifecoach 提醒配置
  ```yaml
  lifecoach:
    daily_checkin:
      enabled: true
      time: "08:00"
      requires: ["current.daily"]
    weekly_review:
      enabled: true
      day: sunday
      time: "20:00"
  ```

